{"tid":636621,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"經常企係地鐵車廂門口既人入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-04-21T05:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T14:07:15.000Z","uid":175056,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96fd5b4631fcf361ab617f4298938d2d33e88028","tid":636621,"uid":175056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"如果車廂滿人 行唔到入去<br />\n感就正常嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我想講好多時車廂無人<br />\n企撚曬門口 唔比人出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別啊叔同師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到人地衝入車廂個陣都唔知企邊<br />\n<br />\n其實你搭公共交通  可唔可以比返小小同理心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔只係地鐵 其他交通工具都係"},{"pid":"5b668868269a6c30ad84ba04c0d212dd45bdf449","tid":636621,"uid":21385,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:14:24.000Z","msg":"坐都冇得坐<br />\n連企邊都要你管？"},{"pid":"979bb745d300ff80491c0cec65e93aaaaadd243f","tid":636621,"uid":25502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"通常唔理照行撞鳩佢地"},{"pid":"e16584f9c136ec1220f183092063d46b6c8a7dbe","tid":636621,"uid":132698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"不如訪問下d慢動作咁落車既仆街先啦<br />\n明明隔離度門仲多人<br />\n點知呢度有幾條茂利慢慢襟電話<br />\n好似賭神咁慢慢行出黎<br />\n搞到隔離都上哂呢邊先開始入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4733b23148004655b00d1bceb5213eff0cb517","tid":636621,"uid":147367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"明明見到有人想入都唔肯行入去塞住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又無理由推佢前面啲人"},{"pid":"4fadfc458597586712ff519a7a80db1aa0931c68","tid":636621,"uid":132698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b668868269a6c30ad84ba04c0d212dd45bdf449","tid":636621,"uid":21385,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T0